Package gal4j.algorithm

Class Population

java.lang.Object
gal4j.algorithm.Population
public class Population extends Object
Represents a population of chromosomes in a genetic algorithm. This class manages a list of chromosomes, tracks the generation number, and provides utility methods for fitness evaluation, sorting, and statistics. It supports both sequential and parallel fitness evaluation.
Author:
Filip Křenek
